text: Matamata is a town in Waikato, North Island, New Zealand. It may subsequently refer to: * Matamata-Piako District, territorial authority for Matamata * Matamata Airport * Matamata College, secondary school * Matamata Swifts, football club * Matamata (New Zealand electorate), former parliamentary electorate
title: Matamata, New Zealand (disambiguation)
